Captain, you've got an hour and a half.

171
00:19:47,563 --> 00:19:50,555
He's, uh, thinking, Foster.

172
00:19:50,632 --> 00:19:53,157
You know, something
you were paid to do ?

173
00:19:54,636 --> 00:19:58,834
You thinking
what l'm thinking ? Huh ?

174
