- ( Laughing )
- What ?

175
00:20:01,810 --> 00:20:04,870
Salvage ? Salvage, baby.

176
00:20:04,947 --> 00:20:08,747
( Chuckling )
You all signed on for a percentage.

177
00:20:08,817 --> 00:20:11,980
But you never figured
l'd bring you this, did you ?

178
00:20:12,054 --> 00:20:14,454
